===Etymology===
First attested in 1528. From {{der|en|xno|abeiance||legal expectation}}, from {{der|en|fro|abeance||desire}} from {{m|fro|abeer|abeër|to gape at, aspire after}}, {{m|fro|abaer}}, {{m|fro|abair||to desire}}, from {{m|fro|a||to}} + {{m|fro|baer|baër|to gape}},<ref>{{R:American Heritage Dictionary|edition=1971|page=3}}</ref> {{m|fro|bair||yawn}}, from {{bor|en|ML.|batō||to yawn}}<ref>{{R:MW3 1976|page=3}}</ref><ref>{{R:CDOE|page=2}}</ref>.

